reviewText: Terrible Quality, Story, Overall, a BIG Minus of a Deal.  Worst Example Ever. Stay Away from This Deal.  Super Bad Bad

Very good documentary,  I gave it 5 stars because I'm a Dragracer/fan.
The title list 1958 hot rod magazine car show,  but it's really about
following two drag race teams driving across the U.S. going to small drag race
meets. Then on to the big NHRA Nats in Detroit 1959.
